data.description:
$10,000 Buyer Incentive with accepted offer by 31 December 2023!  Loan Assumption Option available on 4.5% interest rate loan for qualified VA Buyers! This home is zoned for Highland Elementary School which offers a Dual immersion Program to upcoming Kindergarteners. Just one more perk to living in this amazing home!  Entering the home you are welcomed by an open staircase, formal Dining Room and large living room with vaulted ceilings that open up to the second floor overlook. This home features a main floor owners suite and laundry room. A second floor study, guest room, bonus room, and two additional bedrooms  & full bathroom.
The Large covered front porch is perfect for those fall evenings with the glow from the Christmas Tree glistening in your favorite glass of wine!  Enjoy all this back yard has to offer with the covered screened in deck that leads to an uncovered deck and swings, the perfect spot to entertain!!
